     this relationship with the relationship ` A C_ B ` (as defined in
     ~ df-ss ).  Other possible definitions are given by ~ dfpss2 and
     ~ dfpss3 .  (Contributed by NM, 7-Feb-1996.) $)
  df-pss $a |- ( A C. B <-> ( A C_ B /\ A =/= B ) ) $.

